posting_body: ['Toni Hill', '| The Apartment Resource |', 'show contact info', 'Lyndale Ave S, Minneapolis, MN', '$1930/month', 'Bedrooms: 2', 'Bathrooms: 1', '900  Sq Footage', 'Parking: $125 Garage Parking', 'Pet Policy: Dogs & Cats OK', 'Deposit $300', 'Lease Term: 12-18 Months', 'Offering the excitement of Uptown, alongside the peacefulness of a residential neighborhood.', 'Our amenities provide residents with resort-style living while effortlessly embracing their active lifestyles with our adjacency to the Greenway.', 'Featuring full gourmet kitchens available in 3 finishes, stainless Energy-Star appliances, granite countertops and backsplash, roomy and walk in closets, extra storage, wide plank hardwood floors with Berber bedroom carpeting or concrete floors throughout.', 'Prices and availability are subject to change.', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'Apartment Amenities', 'LED lighting', 'Stainless steel appliances', 'Granite countertops', 'Walk-in closets *', 'Full-size washer and dryer', 'Balconies *', 'Community Amenities', 'Indoor saltwater pool', 'Outdoor patio', 'Outdoor fireplace', 'Outdoor grilling station', 'Zen garden with water features', 'Fitness center', 'Art gallery', 'Conference room', 'Tea bar', 'Boutique lobby', 'Club room', 'Dog run', 'Pet spa', 'Carwash', 'Rooftop terrace', 'Ramp to Midtown Greenway Corridor', 'Bicycle storage & repair shop', "Children's play area", 'Green design', 'Contact:', 'Toni Hill', 'The Apartment Resource', 'show contact info']
